    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "counselors and advisors arent gonna fix the fact that i'm just drowning. every time i try to fix one thing another thing breaks. it's just a constant cycle of losing. it feels less like a \"financial problem\" and more like my entire life is just... broken. i'm just exhausted from trying to find a way out that doesn't exist.",
